# Whitelist: this package must only ever hold hand-picked config.
# Everything else in ~/.claude (secrets, caches, transcripts, plugins,
# projects, sessions, logs) stays machine-local and is never tracked.
*
!.gitignore
!settings.json
!settings.local.json
!keybindings.json
# Add more as needed, e.g.:
# !CLAUDE.md
# !commands/
# !agents/
